sufficient to maintain these Possessions, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> It is true, the <HI>Dutch,</HI> an <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> though a small People, maintain their <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> But we may observe, they never <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> far from their natural and tradin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> Water.</P>
