<P><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">, where the Drawings are just and pertin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">t, are Beauties in H<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">ory. I have no private Pique against Mr. <HI>Kn&mdash;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"></HI>&punc; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> I <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> my self in insulting the Authority with which he is vested <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Ma<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ness in the <HI>West-India</HI> Is<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ands perhap<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> to a late Act of Parliament against <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> late Frenzy Fit in <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> <HI>England.</HI></P></NOTE> <HI>Knowles</HI> made a general <HI>Imp<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ss</HI>
